      "delta": [
        "Baseline: serverless-no-VPC, ~$0 idle floor",
        "Single-region; SNS + SQS are managed-HA but no explicit multi-AZ redundancy layer",
        "HMAC signature + 5-min replay guard on ingest Lambda",
        "SNS → 2 SQS queues (extensible to N) for independent per-consumer retry buffers",
        "DynamoDB on-demand absorbs write spikes; TTL cleans dedup window automatically",
        "DLQ on each SQS queue; consumers tagged idempotent-consumer",
        "Alarms on error rate, throttles, DLQ depth → SNS → email"
      ],
      "tradeoffs": [
        "Single-region: SNS/SQS/Lambda are managed-HA within a region but no cross-region DR",
        "No provisioned Lambda concurrency — cold starts possible on sudden spike (mitigated by SQS buffering)",
        "DLQ messages require manual redrive or operator intervention; no automated replay"
      ],
